parameters:
--Stamina and skill power have been \c[24]fully
restored\c[0]!

--! Is this the ritual chamber of the lava cave!? Just
breathing in here feels like it's scorching my throat
because of the lava's heat.

...It seems it took us longer than expected to get to this
ritual chamber.

Heh heh heh. Welcome to my stronghold, the Fuji Lava Cave--
I'm honored you've come to witness the great eruption of
Mount Fuji at the risk of your lives.

Kokuyou Tengu! Your ambition ends here! I will not allow
someone who disrupts the natural order as the king of
apparitions--and for leading Senbi into the path of demons!
I will surely end your life right here!

I cannot forgive you for using my father as a pawn. Be
prepared.

Ha ha! This is not peaceful at all, is it?♪ I'm not fond of
fighting, so I'll leave this place to the strongest warrior,
the vengeful ghost.
Vengeful ghost--? Is there still one left...!?

Now that all eight vengeful war demons have been defeated,
my last trump card. You could say it's the guardian deity of
this Fuji Lava Cave. Come forth [Vengeful Ghost. Phantom]--!
～～～～!? Is that person, could it be--!?

You seem to remember him as someone from the same village,
Momiji-san. Yes. This vengeful ghost, Phantom, is your
uncle, Chutarou-dono.
--! Could it be that vengeful ghost is Karin's father...!?

What...? You were Chutarou-dono's daughter? This is quite a
surprise. There's no falsehood in your bloodline. No wonder
you are strong...

...Oh, you don't seem to be surprised that your real father
was killed and turned into such a grotesque form? This is
unexpected--

...I just had memories flood into my head. What happened in
this lava cave five years ago... It seems I come from a
pretty amazing line of shrine maidens.

(I see, it must be because of the exorcist Miko
blood that Karin carries...)

So it is. I thought the bloodline of the demon-sealing
exorcist shrine maidens had completely died out while I was
hiding from the world... Such a troublesome and tenacious
lineage. Now that I've heard this, there's no need for
mercy! I'll finish you off right here!

Father! Don't you recognize me? Are you really being
controlled by him to the very core of your heart...?
That move! Is it Karin's signature battle technique!?

～～～～!! (A technique faster and more intense than Triple Wind
Fang...! It's definitely father's secret move...)

Karin, if you cannot fight, would it be alright for us three
to battle instead?

My chest feels tight with strong emotions... but I'll fight
and awaken you. Here I go, father--I'll show you how much
I've grown!
What!? To defeat the strongest vengeful demon--!

Now! To stop the eruption of Mount Fuji, I will destroy this
altar, Momiji!

--Masaki and Momiji's attack has blown the altar to
smithereens!
Wha-!? The altar is... shattered to pieces!?
--Our chance! I'll take your life now, Gyouon!
We did it! Yugiri-san's sword has pierced the heart!
No--! That one is a fake!

The decoy demon--!? It's not the real Gyouon! When did they
switch places!?

Fufufu... The ritual is already perfectly complete. That
altar, which was used for many years to gather malice, is
now like the empty shell of a cicada after molting.
Destroying it is meaningless.
--! Gyouon's voice? Where are you right now!?

We are far above this lava cave, at the crater of Mount
Fuji's summit. If you wish to recklessly witness the grand
eruption from the best seat in the house, please do not
hesitate to come. We welcome you♪

Nuuuu! Damn you, Gyouon, mocking us...! Let's head there at
once, everyone!
Dad, do you... recognize me? Please... wake up...

...Karin. You must have seen the vengeful demons we defeated
on our way here. Unfortunately... only the dead can become
vengeful demons.
Dad, you really were dead... I'm sorry, I didn't realize...

Five years ago... ever since Dad suddenly disappeared...
I've been searching for you. I thought maybe if I became
famous, Dad might come back, so I even called myself the
Phantom Thief Mouse Komachi...
--Dad! Please, just say something back to me!
No way...? Is this, Dad's... spirit...?

You've done well to come this far, Karin... Did you chase
after me because you wanted to see me? You're quite the
daughter...

I am your father. You've grown up. Although my consciousness
was hazy as I was controlled by Gyouon, I vaguely remember
our battle. That was a splendid strike that surpassed my
secret technique, Fivefold Wind Fang, Karin.

Everything! Everything I learned was from you, Dad! Because
you were there... I...!

Don't cry, Karin--I am very happy to see that you have grown
up to be a strong and sturdy daughter. The crybaby infant
has truly become strong...

Before you were born, I killed many people as a ninja...
Becoming the righteous thief Mouse Kozo in Edo was my way
of atoning for those deeds.

Stealing koban from corrupt rich men and giving it to the
struggling common folk--I never thought the skills I honed
as a ninja during the warring states period would benefit
so many people. I was happy. It felt like a calling in a
time of peace.

It seems my time has come to be fetched... I want to ascend
the slopes of Yomi with the joy of having seen my daughter's
growth. Let us part in this life with smiles on our faces,
as father and daughter--
Yeah... I understand... I won't cry anymore...

Momiji is here too. She took care of you when you were a
baby. Please send my regards to Kotaro--

Karin. With your current self, you should understand what
you must do... My proud daughter, Karin, together with Kolin
--thank you. Farewell--
Yeah...! Thank you for everything, Dad...!
Chutaro's soul ascended peacefully to heaven--!

Hmm. To think that he was turned into a vengeful demon by
Gyouon's forbidden arts, yet returned to his original pure
spirit as a human... I have lived long, but this is the
first time I've witnessed such a miracle.

Karin... It's regrettable that the father you were searching
for had passed away... but it's good that you were able to
talk to him in the end.

Yeah... Sorry everyone, for making you wait... Let's hurry
to the crater at the summit of Mount Fuji where Gyouon is--

There is a door beyond the destroyed altar. Surely it leads
to the summit.

All right! The next battle is truly the last one! Let's go
with full spirit--!
--! (An extraordinary sense of unease!? What lies ahead...!)

Phew...hah...! I-I'm okay...just got a little dizzy from the
heat of the lava...thank you, Momiji-san.

(...I may not have the ability to sense demons like Karin,
but even so, I can feel it clearly. There's a formidable
demon ahead.)

Hmm. It seems we're close to the enemy's stronghold. Is
everyone ready?

...Yes. We've come this far, there's no turning back now.
We'll defeat Gyōon and stop the rampage of Mount Fuji.

My wish is... to ensure that no one else has to live a life
dedicated solely to slaying demons and seeking revenge on
them, like I have.

Similarly--to eradicate the root of all calamities here and
now, so that no human will ever suffer from becoming a demon
for all eternity.

(Karin, Yugiri, Momiji--they are all about to confront their
archenemy in order to overcome their own karma... However,
Gyōon is strong. Even I may not come out of this unscathed.
No matter the outcome, I must fight with all my heart and
soul...)

--? Is that a Qilin!? Even such a formidable mythical beast
is here!

If we defeat those two, it seems we can proceed to the next
mechanism.

Whether it's a Qilin or an elephant, it doesn't matter!
Anything that stands in our way right now will be crushed
with full force! Let's go, everyone!

Yes! Time is of the essence. Let's break through in one fell
swoop!!
--Karin was enveloped in a mysterious light!
--Hang in there, Karin! Are you awake?
Thank goodness... It seems like Karin-chan has come to.

What's this, you don't remember anything? We were all
worried because you suddenly collapsed.

Strangely... from the past... the events of the last five
years started flooding into my mind... My father's
memories... they've all been transmitted to me...

Yes. Just ahead is the ritual site where Gyōon resides.
Let's hurry and destroy the altar. If we do, the eruption of
Mount Fuji should stop--
